description: Gets the primary and secondary connection strings for the namespace.

resource_group_name.description: Name of the Resource group within the Azure subscription.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials that uniquely identify a Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

keyname.description: A string that describes the authorization rule.

secondaryconnectionstring.description: Secondary connection string of the created namespace authorization rule.

aliasprimaryconnectionstring.description: Primary connection string of the alias if GEO DR is enabled

aliassecondaryconnectionstring.description: Secondary  connection string of the alias if GEO DR is enabled

primarykey.description: A base64-encoded 256-bit primary key for signing and validating the SAS token.

secondarykey.description: A base64-encoded 256-bit primary key for signing and validating the SAS token.

primaryconnectionstring.description: Primary connection string of the created namespace authorization rule.
